#compdef caddy-l4
# Documentation: https://github.com/mholt/caddy-l4
# Reference accessed: 2026-05-17
# Verified: upstream docs at the URL above.

# caddy-l4 is a Layer-4 (TCP/UDP) module for Caddy v2; it does NOT ship a
# separate "caddy-l4" CLI. The module is compiled into the regular caddy
# binary via `xcaddy build --with github.com/mholt/caddy-l4` and is then
# invoked through `caddy run` etc. This stub exists only to short-circuit
# completion if some downstream rebrands the binary as `caddy-l4`; refer to
# the _caddy completion for actual subcommands and flags.

_arguments -s -S \
  '(- *)'{-h,--help}'[show help]' \
  '(- *)'{-v,--version}'[show version]' \
  '*::caddy command:_caddy'
